chunk_content: As with all children and families enrolled in the comprehensive program, it is critical to remind graduating C/ALHIV and their caregivers that they can re-enroll at any time that they are not meeting the benchmarks. Figure 4: Minimum Required Graduation Benchmarks 59 Exited or Transferred: • Data reported into the Exited or Transferred disaggregate should only include individuals exiting P R or transferring from the OVC Comprehensive program. However, the Exited or Transferred E disaggregate will not be included in the OVC Comprehensive total. The OVC Comprehensive total V includes only active and graduated program participants. E N • At Q2: Report the number of children and caregivers that exited or transferred from the OVC T program in previous 2 quarters. At Q4: Report the number of children and caregivers that exited I O or transferred from the OVC program in the past 4 quarters.
